  <description>
    Simple podcast app built with Electron. Play your favorite podcasts, and discover new ones with an easy to use interface.
    <ul>
      <li>Listen to our favorite podcasts</li>
      <li>Search for podcasts and subscribe directly from the app</li>
      <li>Add episodes to playlists</li>
      <li>Filter episodes by their duration and release date</li>
      <li>Export/import podcasts (.opml)</li>
    </ul>
  </description>
